title: Capital Bikeshare membership by Zip Code
name: Capital Bikeshare membership by Zip Code
description:
The number of Capital Bikeshare subscribers by Zipcode in Washington DC as of April 9, 2011.

The original data had all zipcodes - but this just lists DC zipcode locations.

Found via http://www.washingtoncitypaper.com/blogs/housingcomplex/2011/04/20/calling-all-bikeshare-geeks/
